# New Contributor Guide — TerraLedger

Welcome to TerraLedger! This guide gives you a complete overview of the project, how it's organized, and how to make your first contribution.

---

## What is TerraLedger?

TerraLedger is a verified carbon credit marketplace built on Stellar/Soroban. Carbon projects mint tokenized Real World Assets (RWAs), corporations buy and permanently retire them on-chain, and every credit carries a full provenance trail from issuance to retirement.

**The problem it solves:** The voluntary carbon market is riddled with fraud, double-counting, and greenwashing. VerdeChain makes all of that mathematically impossible — credits have unique serial numbers, retirements are irreversible on-chain, and the full audit trail is publicly readable without a wallet.

