## Repository Layout

```
verdechain/
├── contracts/        ← Rust/Soroban smart contracts (START HERE for blockchain work)
├── backend/          ← NestJS REST API + PostgreSQL
├── frontend/         ← Next.js 14 web app
├── oracle/           ← Python oracle bridge (satellite + price feeds)
├── scripts/          ← Setup, deploy, and test scripts
├── docs/             ← You are here
└── .github/          ← CI/CD workflows
```

---

## How the Layers Connect

```
Frontend (Next.js)
    │
    ├── Freighter Wallet → signs transactions
    ├── @stellar/stellar-sdk → submits txs to Stellar
    │
    └── Backend API (NestJS) → reads/writes PostgreSQL
            │
            └── Stellar RPC → reads on-chain state
                    │
                    └── Soroban Contracts (Rust)
                            │
                            └── Oracle (Python) → pushes off-chain data on-chain
```

