## Smart Contracts Overview

| Contract | What it does |
|---|---|
| `verde_registry` | Project registration, verification, status management |
| `verde_credit` | Mint, transfer, retire credits with serial numbers |
| `verde_marketplace` | List, buy, bulk purchase credits for USDC |
| `verde_oracle` | Receive satellite monitoring and price feed data |

